Time to First Working (Requirements to first runnable outcome): ~1 Day (Clarification + Coding).

Total Dev Time (Requirement -> code completed -> PR): ~1 to 1.5 Days total.

Time spent per phase:
 
Requirement clarification: 1 to 2 hours.

Implementation: Max 1 Day (Manual coding).

Fixing Bugs/Rework: 1 to 3 hours.

Testing/Validation: 30 minutes to 1 hour.

Number of iterations before "Acceptable": 0 to 1 iteration.

Time per change (Small change -> how long to implement + test): Less than 2 hours.

Bug Categories:

Logic Errors: Yes.

Missed Requirements: No.

Config/integration errors: No.

Regression Issue: No.

Time Spent Debugging: 15 to 30 minutes.

Bus Factor (If primary Dev is out, how long does it take someone else to take over?): High/Slow.

Documentation Quality: Low/Delayed.

Consistency in implementation: 90-95%.

Manual Testing: 30 minutes to 1 hour.

Effort Split % coding vs rework: 80% Coding / 20% Rework.

After, i.e. with spec based development:

Time to First Working Requirements to first runnable outcome: ~2 to 2.5 Hours (Clarification + Spec Prep + Generation).

Total Dev Time (Requirement -> code completed -› PR): ~3 to 5 Hours total.

Time spent per phase:

Requirement clarification: 1 to 2 hours.

Implementation: 30 to 50 minutes (Includes 15-30 mins defining/writing requirements for the agent + 15-20 mins generation time).

Fixing Bugs/Rework: ~10 minutes (Regenerating files).

Testing/Validation: 30 minutes to 1 hour.

Number of iterations before "Acceptable": 2 to 3 iterations.

Time per change (Small change -> how long to implement + test): Less than 10 minutes.

Bug Categories:

Logic Errors: Rare.

Missed Requirements: High initially (Requires re-prompting).

Config/integration errors: Yes (Schema mapping/paths).

Regression Issue: No.

Time Spent Debugging: 5 to 10 minutes (Quick ID, but manual verify required).

Bus Factor (If primary Dev is out, how long does it take someone else to take over?): Low/Fast.

Documentation Quality: High/Instant.

Consistency in implementation: 100%.

Manual Testing: 30 minutes to 1 hour.

Effort Split % coding vs rework: 10% Coding / 90% Spec Definition & Rework.
